        "$:/plugins/tongerner/exploration/macros/codefilter": {
            "created": "20140728113918255",
            "text": "\\define codefilter(filter, state)\n<$select tiddler='$:/state/$state$/list'>\n<$list filter=\"$filter$\">\n<option><$view field='title'/></option>\n</$list>\n</$select>\n\n''Tiddler:'' <$tiddler tiddler={{$:/state/$state$/list}}>\n<$link to={{$:/state/$state$/list}}>\n\n<$view field=\"title\"/>\n</$link>\n''Source code:''\n<pre><$view field=\"text\"/></pre>\n<hr>\n''Renders as:''\n<$tiddler tiddler={{$:/state/$state$/list}}>\n<$transclude mode='block'/>\n</$tiddler>\n<hr>\n''Fields:''\n<$transclude tiddler=\"$:/core/ui/TiddlerFields\"/>\n\\end\n\n```\n\\define codefilter(filter, state)\n<$select tiddler='$:/state/$state$/list'>\n<$list filter=\"$filter$\">\n<option><$view field='title'/></option>\n</$list>\n</$select>\n\n''Tiddler:'' <$tiddler tiddler={{$:/state/$state$/list}}>\n<$link to={{$:/state/$state$/list}}>\n\n<$view field=\"title\"/>\n</$link>\n''Source code:''\n<pre><$view field=\"text\"/></pre>\n<hr>\n''Renders as:''\n<$tiddler tiddler={{$:/state/$state$/list}}>\n<$transclude mode='block'/>\n</$tiddler>\n<hr>\n''Fields:''\n<$transclude tiddler=\"$:/core/ui/TiddlerFields\"/>\n\\end\n```\n",
